reviewText: such a great actor and such a great voice! these movies always remind me of mi lindo y querido Mexico!
I Love these old classic Vicente Fernandez movies...I like the collection of the 4 movies, specially for the price...cant beat that.
Dvds are great quality and old school. Nothing like a classic Vicente Movie. They are all sealed and packaged in one box.
Las mejores peliculas de vicente fernandez, se las recomiendo comprenlas todas. Son comp un tesoro que durara para siempre. Gracias
Wish item description had gone little further, as this was not was I expected, this is a set of Vicente Fernandez movies, not videoclips or concerts.
